title: Secrets of the Great Masters (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
Secrets of the Great Masters
G. P. Putnam's Sons | 1964 | English | 220 pages | PDF | 40.6 MB

An attempt has been made in the pages that follow to present some account of the main features and of the results from exploration using the techniques of our day and age with reference to the art of painting. The comments provide some form of written record of the television series which roused such wide interest, the author assuming sole responsibility for the views stated. The aim has been to sign-post a stage that has been reached in research, rather than a summary which would be premature at this juncture
